  <summary date="2022-02-04T19:24:38Z" status="Introduced in House">Witness Security and Protection Grant Program Act of 2021

 This bill directs the Department of Justice to award competitive matching grants to state, local, and tribal governments to establish or maintain witness protection programs in cases involving (1) a homicide, serious violent felony, or serious drug offense; or (2) gangs or organized crime.</summary>
